    <thetext>Description of problem:

xorg-x11-server-devel-1.19.0-0.3.20161026.fc25.x86_64 ships
/usr/include/xorg/dixfontstr.h which has #include &lt;X11/fonts/libxfont2.h&gt; 
but the xorg-x11-server-devel package does not require libxfont2-devel

I got a compilation error because of this when trying to build the xorg qxl driver which includes this header.</thetext>
